    "text": "$$\n\\text{Số trung bình: } \\bar{x} = \\frac{8 \\cdot 6,75 + 10 \\cdot 7,25 + 16 \\cdot 7,75 + 24 \\cdot 8,25 + 13 \\cdot 8,75 + 7 \\cdot 9,25 + 4 \\cdot 9,75}{82} = \\frac{666}{82} \\approx 8,122.\n$$"
